track_notes: Boggy in places this walk, but actually less than one mile with a mere 550 feet of ascent. You could set up by the fence corner at NY 7833 3761 as this is well within the activation zone, but there is little cover there from wind.
track_title: Burnhope Seat direct route from B6277

track_notes:
You can use this longer route up or down and check out the facilities of the Yad Moss Ski Club. It makes for a more interesting circular walk. 
73 Phil G4OBK
track_title: Burnhope Seat via Yad moss Ski Club
